__a01580d4-b89e-4e40-a1d1-437c998d2c9c-1683121453856f019b-1":{"type":"bl_text","settings":{"col_dk":"12","col_tb":"12","text_size":"40,15","txt_align":"start","sub_heading":"","heading":"5 Not-to-Miss Saree Looks of Aishwarya, Trisha Krishnan & Sobhita Dhulipala in Cult-Movie Ponniyin Selvan (PS-I) ","text":"<p><strong>T<\/strong>he greatest of all time - that's what people are saying about the latest cult movie from the house of Mani Ratnam - yes, you guessed it right I am talking of <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Ponniyin_Selvan:_I\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Ponniyin Selvan<\/strong><\/em><\/a><em><strong>.<\/strong><\/em>The conflict between Chola princess <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Kundavai_Pir%C4%81ttiy%C4%81r\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Kundavai<\/strong><\/em><\/a>(Trisha Krishnan) and <a href=\"http:\/\/ponniiyinselvanbysumi.blogspot.com\/p\/nandini-character-sketch.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Nandini<\/strong><\/em><\/a>(Aishwarya Rai), the queen of Pazhuvur, is expected to be one of the many pivotal moments which got witnessed by the spectators across the world in <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Mani_Ratnam\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mani Ratnam’s <\/strong><\/em><\/a>Ponniyin Selvan -1, which released on September 30, worldwide.This Tamil classic has stolen the breath of many. Fans are loving the glorified version of Kalki’s Ponniyin Selvan on the big screen. This historical fiction movie features an ensemble cast of Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Jayam Ravi, Karthi, Trisha, Aishwarya Lekshmi, Sobhita Dhulipala and several other veteran actors. But what attracted most of the women who had watched the feature film - is the timeless saree collections prepared by<a href=\"https:\/\/www.telegraphindia.com\/entertainment\/ps-i-costume-designer-eka-lakhani-on-working-with-mani-ratnam-and-styling-her-muse-ranveer-singh\/cid\/1892581\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Costume Designer Eka Lakhani<\/strong><\/em><\/a>.So, today I thought to take to my blog to scribble about the<strong>PS I<\/strong>saree looks that mesmerised so many.<\/p>","subhd_color":"#222222","hd_color":"#222222","des_color":"#878787","use_shadow":false,"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","open_link":"_blank","btn_icon":false,"button_style":"default","btn_size":"large","btn_cl":"dark","button_effect":"default"}}},"block_order":["template--16762872660201__a01580d4-b89e-4e40-a1d1-437c998d2c9c-1683121453856f019b-1"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center","top_heading":"","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"space_h_item":"20","space_v_item":"10","space_h_item_mb":"20","space_v_item_mb":"10","layout":"t4s-container-wrap","cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,50px,","pd":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"8b2c4452-e48f-46da-91a3-ea79887dc7af":{"type":"image_text","blocks":{"template--16762872660201__8b2c4452-e48f-46da-91a3-ea79887dc7af-1683121453856f019b-0":{"type":"bl_image","settings":{"image1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ps-2.webp","col_dk":"6","col_tb":"6","layout_des":"carousel","post_mobile":"default","image_ratio":"ratioadapt","image_size":"cover","image_position":"8","loop":true,"au_time":0,"au_hover":true,"nav_btn":false,"btn_vi":"hover","btn_owl":"default","btn_shape":"none","btn_cl":"dark","btn_size":"small","btn_hidden_mobile":true,"nav_dot":false,"dot_owl":"default","dots_cl":"dark","dots_round":true,"dots_space":10,"dots_hidden_mobile":false}},"template--16762872660201__8b2c4452-e48f-46da-91a3-ea79887dc7af-1683121453856f019b-1":{"type":"bl_text","settings":{"col_dk":"6","col_tb":"6","text_size":"40,15","txt_align":"start","sub_heading":"","heading":"#1. Royal Touch of Tanjore Silks - Trisha's Look ","text":"<p>The Chola princess Kundavai is portrayed as a strong and courageous woman. Her personality is reflected in her costumes that are sculpted, with strong lines.<br\/><br\/>Like the Tanjore silks she is seen wearing in most of the scenes are made from silk in Thanjavur with vibrant colours and are apt for any occasion. Tanjore silk sarees represent ethnicity and beauty and have temple style architecture designs on their broad borders. <\/p>","subhd_color":"#222222","hd_color":"#222222","des_color":"#878787","use_shadow":false,"button_label":"Button label","button_link":"","open_link":"_blank","btn_icon":false,"button_style":"default","btn_size":"large","btn_cl":"dark","button_effect":"default"}}},"block_order":["template--16762872660201__8b2c4452-e48f-46da-91a3-ea79887dc7af-1683121453856f019b-0","template--16762872660201__8b2c4452-e48f-46da-91a3-ea79887dc7af-1683121453856f019b-1"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center","top_heading":"","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"space_h_item":"20","space_v_item":"10","space_h_item_mb":"20","space_v_item_mb":"10","layout":"t4s-container-wrap","cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,50px,","pd":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"de268ff9-a58c-4341-b1d8-f9f4ed6ce9a3":{"type":"video_featured","settings":{"se_height":"t4s_ratio16_9","custom_dk":true,"height_dk":600,"custom_tb":true,"height_tb":400,"custom_mb":true,"height_mb":250,"source":"1","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=D4qAQYlgZQs","file_link":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0610\/5209\/2628\/files\/Share_your_brand_story_by_adding_a_video_to_your_store.mp4?v=1641630446","au_video":false,"loop_video":true,"bg_overlay":"#000000","bg_opacity":0,"layout":"t4s-se-container","cl_bg":"","cl_bg_gradient":"","mg":",,50px,","pd":"","mg_mb":",,30px,","pd_mb":"","use_cus_css":false,"code_cus_css":""}},"398dcd1c-2be0-4a33-b723-52dde31126de":{"type":"image_text","blocks":{"template--16762872660201__398dcd1c-2be0-4a33-b723-52dde31126de-1683121453856f019b-1":{"type":"bl_text","settings":{"col_dk":"12","col_tb":"12","text_size":"40,15","txt_align